# `index.html` navigation

The app lives in a single large `index.html` (markup, CSS, and script). Before editing or debugging, **locate the right region by searching** (workspace search or editor find):

| Marker | Where | Typical use |
|--------|--------|----------------|
| `=== ` | HTML comments | Head assets, stylesheet blocks, page shell, modal, script tag |
| `// ---` | JavaScript | State, modal, parsers, persistence, scheduler, render, event wiring |
| `/* ---` | CSS | Tokens, header, panels, table, modal, print |

The file banner after `<!DOCTYPE html>` restates these patterns. Prefer **jumping to a section** over reading the file linearly.
